//
// test/sema/width/slice_expr.test — bit-slice expression width
// fixture (T024 rollover; specs/006-m3-sema/tasks.md Phase 4a). Per
// S15 (lang.ebnf:877) bit-slice indices `[hi:lo]` must be compile-
// time constants; the result width is `hi - lo + 1`. Asserts the
// `SliceExpr` carries a `: BitVector(N)` Type suffix per
// `emit-ast-format.contract.md` Invariant 2.

// RUN: printf 'module m {\n  wire a[8];\n  reg q = a[3:0];\n}\n' > %t.nsl
// RUN: %nslc -emit=ast %t.nsl | FileCheck %s

// CHECK: (RegDecl {{.*}}name=q
// CHECK: (SliceExpr {{.*}} : BitVector({{[0-9]+}})
